you because I believe he's a good man and I want him

10:52.932 --> 10:59.602
to be with a good man. Well, tell me, where were you 
born, Uncle Bob? I was born not far from this place,

11:02.907 --> 11:09.516
up here south, west of here, about five miles. And 
how old are you? Well, now, I told you about over the

11:11.748 --> 11:17.395
December, 7th of summer, two or three. My daddy 
told me I was 19 years old on the 18th of December.

11:27.406 --> 11:28.948
