myself.

19:56.002 --> 19:57.204
And how'd you learn to read? Well, he learned at 
night. He said he wasn't no educated man. He could

20:01.829 --> 20:05.474
just read print, and he'd sit up at night and teach 
his children. That's the way we learned. I heard a

20:09.884 --> 20:15.793
story about a judge asking a colored boy on the 
witness stand. He said, Jim, can you read writing?

20:19.759 --> 20:21.221
He said, no, sir, judge. I can't even read reading. 
But you can read reading and write and go. And they

20:31.637 --> 20:37.967
had a preacher who was trying to make a preacher out 
of him. And I asked him, could he, did he know, did he

20:38.521 --> 20:41.825
know theology? He said, no, sir, I never knew that 
man in my life. I never been crazy with him. So I

20:49.535 --> 20:53.019
don't know about no, nothing like that. How old 
were you when you joined the church? I was 19 years

20:59.908 --> 21:05.675
old. And how old were you when you got married? Oh. 
Just in between it. Just started in between it.

21:13.470 --> 21:15.673
Well, did your wife make you join the church? No, 
sir. Let's join myself. Let's tuck a motion and

21:18.758 --> 21:20.681
join myself. Well, how have you got along so well in 
life? What's been your principles? Well, people

21:27.231 --> 21:29.054
are after people. Anybody you know around here 
hasn't bought my principles. I just went on. I just

21:34.201 --> 21:39.010
like and know what a right to do and I always try to do 
what's right.

21:43.037 --> 21:45.041
Well, that's a mighty good way to do it, Pa. Yes, 
sir. I know what's right and I try my best to do

21:46.003 --> 21:52.435
what's right in everything I do. How many times 
have you voted? Ain't voted but twice. vote for who

21:56.838 --> 22:10.955
she wants, and vote for who the President of

21:56.838 --> 22:10.955
