his self, not to send his son. We got no time to fool

30:23.893 --> 30:27.681
with chillin' here tonight. Come right through 
the cornfield. Don't take time to come all the way

30:30.674 --> 30:35.445
around the road by Mr. John Coleman. Cause these 
mooners are just about ready to come through. Then

30:39.836 --> 30:42.262
the others will join in the prayer by singing. 
